(58, 1, '2023-09-14 18:45:16', '2023-09-14 18:45:16', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p id=\"viewer-foo\">What plans do you have for higher studies? Have you decided yet, what course you plan to pursue? Are you planning to study abroad? Are you deciding the right path for your future?</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p id=\"viewer-db73s\">Alas! So many questions to answer and much to plan and think about! Fret not; these all can be answered, and some solutions can work best for a glorious future. After all, none of us has come so far without these questions in mind. Let us check out this amazing country, Canada, with a lot to offer.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p id=\"viewer-3u8ca\">But why Canada?</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p id=\"viewer-ffknc\">Canada offers a wide range of courses in many disciplines, be it marketing &amp; management, architecture, medicine, arts, nursing, and many more in government as well as private institutions. You must have surely heard about Elon Musk, Malcolm Gladwell, Lily Singh, and Margaret Atwood, some of the renowned names who studied in Canada. Let us list some of the top-ranked universities in Canada:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p id=\"viewer-f5jnh\">• University of Toronto</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p id=\"viewer-2c8lk\">• The University of British Columbia, Vancouver</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p id=\"viewer-a6hmk\">• University of Alberta, Edmonton</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p id=\"viewer-3eief\">• University of Montreal</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p id=\"viewer-cikmu\">• McMaster University</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p id=\"viewer-84jf\">• Western University</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p id=\"viewer-2kgtf\">• University of Calgary</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p id=\"viewer-ci70t\">• University of Waterloo</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p id=\"viewer-2rh2l\">• University of Ottawa</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p id=\"viewer-apntj\">Canada is a vast country with enormous opportunities and a great place to study, offering great prospects. If you are looking for a country that offers good colleges not digging deep into your pockets, Canada gives you that opportunity, as the cost of higher studies is less compared to other countries abroad. Canada is a country that is not expensive to stay in and offers good career options with a high standard of education and a low unemployment rate.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p id=\"viewer-9j42u\">Some of the top educators and academicians are associated with the top most internationally recognized universities. The universities offer high-quality education with excellent internship opportunities. To add, the government policies are quite liberal regarding post-study work and immigration. Another advantage of studying in Canada for international students is the scholarships offered to eligible students, which help reduce the financial burden. Canada also allows studying and working for students pursuing higher studies.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p id=\"viewer-cpv7p\">Scholarships</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p id=\"viewer-2sg08\">Students who excel academically, show exceptional creativity and leadership in school, and can be distinguished from others are applicable for a merit-based scholarship. The school can also nominate students for the University of Toronto\'s Lester B. Pearson International Scholarship.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p id=\"viewer-1alcj\">Research opportunities in Canada</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p id=\"viewer-2rm4h\">One of the important parts of higher education in Canada is Research, which also plays a crucial role in deciding a student to study in Canada. Canadian universities encourage students to come out with unique research ideas and provide monetary benefits in the form of scholarships for research work. In addition, the government and industries give students with exceptional research ideas support to put additional efforts to make it a success. To name a few –medicine, agriculture, computer science, environmental science, and telecom; there are abundant research options available in these fields.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p id=\"viewer-cu4be\">What have you planned once you are through with your studies in Canada?</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p id=\"viewer-anhi5\">Canada offers endless opportunities for all. You can either pursue a higher level of education post your studies or can look for work opportunities. You can work in Canada with a work permit and apply for a Permanent Residency.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p id=\"viewer-egivl\">Permanent Residency in Canada comes with some advantages:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p id=\"viewer-cv7te\">• You become eligible for social benefits just like any Canadian citizen</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p id=\"viewer-6ge6i\">• Canada is one place where you can live, work and study anywhere</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p id=\"viewer-a10r\">• One can apply for Canadian citizenship</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p id=\"viewer-cu0k3\">• Another benefit is protection under Canadian law and the Canadian Charter of Rights and Freedoms.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p id=\"viewer-djan4\">To sum it up, Canada is one country which has been attracting numerous international students from all over the world; a country that offers quality living, good healthcare, a world-recognized education system, and post-study work opportunities.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p id=\"viewer-gs9i\">A great place to study and work</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Why choose Canada for further studies?', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '1-revision-v1', '', '', '2023-09-14 18:45:16', '2023-09-14 18:45:16', '', 1, 'http://localhost/EdCosmo/?p=58', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(59, 1, '2023-09-14 18:54:55', '2023-09-14 18:54:55', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>A welcome change from the College Board, the governing body of the Scholastic Assessment Test (SAT), as it announced conducting of SAT digitally in the next two to three years. These changes are made to reassure the relevance and importance of standardized testing, addressing the concerns that occurred during the Pandemic. International students (non-US-based) will be able to take the test starting from March 2023, while students from the US will have to wait till spring 2024. Tested waters in November 2021, the digital SAT was found to be less stressful by 80 percent of the students and the educators also gave a thumbs up to the change. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The advantages of digital SAT for students will be:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p> • Digital SAT will be shorter offering more time per question. It will be conducted in two hoursinstead of three. There will be shorter reading passages with one question each offering a wide range of topics </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>• Another add-on is the use of calculators for Maths, students will be provided with a built-in calculator or can bring their own </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>• The new Digital SAT will be much more secure and flexible and students will get an inimitable version of the test. There will be flexibility as to when the schools and states will conduct the test. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>• Students will be able to take the test on their personal device or the one issued by the school. Else the center will provide the device. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>• Digital score reports provide more relevant information to students on colleges, career, and training programs. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>• The waiting period for getting the results will reduce to one day from weeks, which in turn will help students to decide on college early. Though many changes have been made, there are a few features that remain the same.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p> • The content of the test and assessment of the knowledge and skills of students will remain the same </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>• The growth tracking of students over time will continue and the scoring will be done earlier on the 1600 scale</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p> • As earlier, the test will be conducted in a test center in the presence of an invigilator • As in the past, students can connect directly to scholarships </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>• The students will get support on accommodation as previously All in all the new digital SAT is projected to offer a great experience to students as well as educators. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>For customising careers with the help of university counsellors, contact Edcosmo Education Advisors, Dr Neeru Bali at 7528002828; www.edcosmo.com</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'ALL YOU WANT TO KNOW ABOUT DIGITAL SAT', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'all-you-want-to-know-about-digital-sat', '', '', '2023-09-14 18:54:56', '2023-09-14 18:54:56', '', 0, 'http://localhost/EdCosmo/?p=59', 0, 'post', '', 0),
